{"tid":1952744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮抗疫小組正研究應否建議民眾戴口罩","createTime":"2020-03-31T19:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T22:50:59.000Z","uid":321748,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa995d6109467d01b956708d598c45c89e79fc9","tid":1952744,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"美國國立過敏症與傳染病研究所所長Anthony Fauci醫生表示，白宮新型肺炎抗疫小組正在研究應否建議民眾使用口罩，以阻截新型冠狀病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\nFauci醫生週二接受CNN訪問時稱，白宮抗疫小組首先要確保，此舉不會令醫護人員失去防護用品的供應。<br />\n<br />\nFauci醫生說：「當我們有充足的口罩供應時，我認為應該要審慎研究應否擴大建議社區使用口罩，不過我們目前仍未到這個地步，但我認為已接近作出定論。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ktsf.com/2020/03/31/white-house-looking-into-broader-use-of-masks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ktsf.com%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2Fwhite-house-looking-into-broader-use-of-masks%2F&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=eda7f7ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ktsf.com/2020/03/31/white-house-looking-into-broader-use-of-masks/</a>"},{"pid":"8da3cf33f246b85c4134ad0c2cb3843d0cda5ce6","tid":1952744,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"黎香港買啦 香港大貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之有錢就有貨 咩認証都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedf84ea4bc136875f2c0664265a20a217c3ea99","tid":1952744,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T20:03:48.000Z","msg":"平民叫佢地用布咪可以囉"},{"pid":"511db2ddee4aaac61f22094ea61891cd9762b4c5","tid":1952744,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T20:06:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔起口罩廠"},{"pid":"fb0d4d69a1d30ce1d053dc84329f4e329a7a3c5c","tid":1952744,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T20:14:41.000Z","msg":"盡快將口罩廠搬返去美國"},{"pid":"c5fe8e35e64f18dc42ba1986d2389824b5a59ceb","tid":1952744